Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.74,0:00:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, we've got trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.98,0:00:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Leukocyte was just fired at Point Delta!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.76,0:00:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the place where Gai is?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.78,0:00:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Leukocyte is a constellation of Quasi-Zenith Satellites.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.24,0:00:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it's completed, it will have full 24-hour coverage directly over Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and be able to strike at any target in our country at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.50,0:00:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would they build something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.97,0:00:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To exterminate the Japanese people.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.38,0:00:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.54,0:00:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right? Are you injured?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.44,0:00:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a few scratches.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.75,0:00:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Kyo and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.30,0:00:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were less fortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.89,0:00:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All our reinforcements were annihilated,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.78,0:00:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the supplies are unrecoverable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.26,0:00:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we take a moment to regroup?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.48,0:00:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. There's no time to waste now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.73,0:01:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll begin our operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{02:48 <eptitle>Cage}{i'm pretty sure this is already in english in the raw}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.63,0:02:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready, Gai?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.62,0:02:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like we're all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The target of this operation is the Leukocyte control facility at the base of the Tsukigase Dam.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to sneak into its bottom floor and stop the control cores.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.22,0:03:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we gonna smash 'em up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenji.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.26,0:03:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yessir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.23,0:03:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Leukocyte.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, it's controlled through a quantum cryptography system on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And 200 meters below the dam, voilà!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.74,0:03:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the control device.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cores are housed in a superconductive float cage,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it switches to autistic mode in response to any physical stimulus.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.96,0:03:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that point it's game over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.26,0:03:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to manipulate it from the outside at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, in order to send this thing the signal to stop,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.04,0:03:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you have to manipulate the cores without touching them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without {\i1}touching{\i0} them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's where Shu and Kenji come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.27,0:03:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their abilities, the King's Right Hand and the gravity-controlling Void,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.99,0:03:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are the keys to this operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, with our reinforcements wiped out...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.27,0:04:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a new proposed plan here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.03,0:04:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our projected casualties are up from 5% to 35%, but it's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking you all to share this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.55,0:04:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying one out of three of us will die?{OH BOY HERE WE GO}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.48,0:04:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.48,0:04:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The danger will spread to this whole country soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice but to contain it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.01,0:04:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone dies because I screw up, won't they die for nothing?{Then don't screw up, nigger.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.22,0:04:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take the blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Kyo and the others, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.98,0:04:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Words are cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.46,0:04:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pulling out of this one.{The best way to get people to not die is to not take part in a crucial mission to stop people from dying.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.24,0:04:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit talking like a spoiled brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.07,0:04:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying this for your sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.51,0:04:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just messed up to follow him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:04:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You little—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.58,0:05:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.25,0:05:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the bad guy here, you or Gai?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.62,0:05:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Read the social cues, man.{autistic mode lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.48,0:05:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.26,0:05:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.78,0:05:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.49,0:05:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There'll be no change of plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.99,0:05:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.80,0:05:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.49,0:05:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you, Inori.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.26,0:05:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for always causing you trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.98,0:05:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they don't listen to {\i1}me{\i0} eith—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.47,0:05:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop talking like that. I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.55,0:05:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do exactly as I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.04,0:06:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leukocyte 3 will transition into its planned orbit in another four hours, and the cage will be complete.{*Might need line splitting}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.83,0:06:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're on standby until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I regret to say it won't be in time, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.61,0:06:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Undertakers will attack in two hours and seventeen minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a private source of information?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, just gut feeling... or perhaps, it's more of a hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is one time I hope your instincts are off, Segai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.24,0:06:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two hours and seventeen minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.81,0:06:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like sundown.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, I see. They'll come at sundown!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.18,0:07:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be your first battle since coming out of the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.62,0:07:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you're talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those little maggots took my Steiner...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make them pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.01,0:07:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they come to me crying and begging for mercy, I'll still pull the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? Did you say something, Lieutenant?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.99,0:07:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, hurry here and show me your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's like first love,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.19,0:07:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Ouma Shu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.74,0:08:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's gotten to me like that in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.50,0:08:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell am I doing all this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, it took all I had just to keep my “leader” act up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.18,0:08:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right after the Leukocyte attack, Kyo was still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.01,0:08:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.03,0:08:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll remember my whole life... that you told me you liked my voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.27,0:08:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My whole life...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:08:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.75,0:09:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was {\i1}smiling{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was glad I was fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,glad that she was the one to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.03,0:09:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I started to ask myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.75,0:09:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Is Tsutsugami Gai someone who can repay their sacrifice?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shouldn't I be better than this?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.25,0:09:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a much smaller man than I let them all believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really nothing... I should be the very first one selected out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.77,0:09:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eavesdropping, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.11,0:10:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have such healthy hobbies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.71,0:10:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.59,0:10:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to see that side of you, Gai.{That's your best response?}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.27,0:10:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of guy did you think I was?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.37,0:10:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You get it now, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.01,0:10:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lose confidence, I get mad, and I let other people spoil me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.97,0:10:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inori, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.03,0:10:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.26,0:10:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I can shoulder everyone's lives and not feel any of their weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.27,0:10:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be indifferent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.51,0:10:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be worthy of everyone's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.79,0:11:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.75,0:11:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.03,0:11:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.30,0:11:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Swan to all units. Open combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.68,0:12:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.74,0:12:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the Undertakers?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.99,0:12:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Major Segai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Send out the Endlave, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.03,0:12:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it! Yes! {\i1}This{\i0} is what Daryl Yan is about!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.27,0:12:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your baby here is a sweet ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.28,0:12:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Steiner... My Steiner...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back! Give it back, give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.51,0:12:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Ogumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.71,0:13:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai, the diversion's coming off pretty well. Are you in yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.03,0:13:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm going to turn off my communicator for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.54,0:13:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pray for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.28,0:13:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.27,0:13:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't fired a single shot, Ouma Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.38,0:13:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all I can do to keep running!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.39,0:13:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and get used to killing people already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.47,0:13:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cores are in here. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.49,0:13:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They just keep coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.07,0:13:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of things here.{Her washboard chest is the ultimate defense against bullets.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Gai?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.17,0:13:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suit yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.74,0:13:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.95,0:13:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.13,0:14:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to kill you if I can avoid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.70,0:14:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So stay back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.23,0:14:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.71,0:14:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.36,0:14:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Inori?! Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.39,0:14:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, quit dawdling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and take it.{SLUT.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for my Void, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's invaded the core room!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.48,0:14:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to swap.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.51,0:14:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, you're so high maintenance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.50,0:14:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then. I believe it's time to go fetch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The center?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.53,0:14:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.03,0:15:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When they've stopped circulating, Funell will input the stop command.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.78,0:15:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello! I've been dying to meet you, Tsutsugami Gai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.05,0:15:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay you back real good for making a fool of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.45,0:15:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just concentrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daryl, the cores are in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go crazy!{fuck this line}{go lazy instead}{I do that all the time}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.26,0:15:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.67,0:16:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.51,0:16:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You piece of shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.78,0:16:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.52,0:16:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, Toku—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.30,0:16:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(634,402)}{16:46 tv screen\bord0\shad0\fs30\blur1} {\c&HE4B6A9&}No Signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.69,0:16:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad news, Gai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's wrong with Leukocyte 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.49,0:16:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damage to the core is making the attitude control malfunction!{yes, attitude}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.98,0:16:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's falling out of orbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.75,0:16:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, Leukocyte 1 will crash in Tokyo with most of its mass intact!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu. Give me the pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.48,0:17:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pen GHQ made you take. Give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.26,0:17:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were on to me, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you got by without pushing it, eh, Ouma?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a bit of a shame, but right now, I'm grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.36,0:17:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Segai?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.50,0:17:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pleased to meet you, Tsutsugami Gai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.76,0:17:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you a deal. I'll use this to do something about the satellite.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange, you erase all the data on Ouma Shu
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that you've gathered from these incidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The signal from your pen is connected to the Leukocyte.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Leukocyte was programmed to fire at it when you pushed the buttons.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.98,0:18:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means if we get the firing satellite, the falling satellite,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and this pen all lined up,{syzygy loool}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.76,0:18:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we should be able to shoot it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,doesn't that mean someone would be making himself the target?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.33,0:18:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai's outside?! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. But right now we need to cover him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.49,0:18:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you just gonna stand by and watch again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.51,0:19:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you okay with that, Ouma Shu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.82,0:19:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to save them, Shu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.23,0:19:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inori?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.76,0:19:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu... do you want to save everyone? And Gai?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.66,0:19:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The fight is on. Will I be the one selected out,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.84,0:19:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}or will it be the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.63,0:20:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Void...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.03,0:20:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone told me to use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you know who, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.00,0:20:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi, how long before they align?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.27,0:20:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thirty seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody hear that? Hold out for thirty seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.86,0:20:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Black Swan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.50,0:20:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.02,0:20:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This isn't my wish alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.78,0:20:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This isn't my power alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.09,0:20:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!{boom}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{21:17 after it comes back on}70-year-old finishes marathon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.77,0:21:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.15,0:21:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come? One sinner is plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.36,0:21:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'd help, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.51,0:21:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this makes me your accomplice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.77,0:21:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Shuichiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.39,0:22:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cocytus trembled.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.04,0:22:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She should awaken any time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.40,0:22:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeking her beloved king...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
